g all reasonable legal expenses, if any. As noted above, prior to"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_9","part":"s1p116","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"lease rescission, and at any point prior to the rescission of this Lease Contract, Fender may cure the breach of this Lease Contract with no additional penalties or consequences by paying all of the late monies due CALIBERT at that time plus 15% interest. Upon the payment of such late monies plus interest, the Lease Contract may not be rescinded."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_9","part":"s1p117","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"If FENDER remains in possession of the WAREHOUSES after the expiration or other termination of the Term, then, at CALIBERT’s option, FENDER shall be deemed to be occupying the WAREHOUSES as a non-fixed term (“tacita reconduccion”) tenant pursuant to Laws, at a monthly rental equal to 115% (1.15) times the monthly rent payable hereunder during the last month of the Term, along with Value Added Tax."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_16","part":"s1p118","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"SIXTH"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_15","part":"s1p118","offsets":[{"start":7,"text":"Current conditions of THE WAREHOUSES"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_16","part":"s1p122","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"SEVENTH"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_15","part":"s1p122","offsets":[{"start":9,"text":"Modifications to TH